name: THE CHILD FROM THE DREAM
description: This work was inspired by a dream I had a few months ago, having a strange dream 7 nights in a row. death, met some dead people i know, getting killed, fight with some strange creatures. This dream started with me sitting in my room then a big pink baby came to me, I was scared and couldn't run, but I didn't think this baby just wanted to hug me, then I woke up. Until now I can't understand what the dream means.
